Title: Gurgaon top cop transferred a fortnight after monster jam
Content: : In what is being seen as a fallout of the massive traffic jam on the Delhi-Gurgaon Expressway over a fortnight ago, the Haryana government on Tuesday transferred Gurgaon Commissioner of Police Navde
Author: Ashok Kumar
